<AUTHOR>Ray Libaad</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I bought this after testing the 550i. outstanding performance. Handles like a sports car but rides like one (19"wheels). Interior is quiet and serene at high speeds. I find myself regularly doing 100-120mph without even feeling it. Exhaust note is sweet. The best low beam headlights in any car I've driven (the road is evenly carpeted with bright white light) but strangely very lousy high beams. Leg room in the front and back is class leading</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>air conditioned seats. adaptive lights. wood finish.</FAVORITE>
